6.00	Bob_Beers_(ice_hockey)	Bob Beers (ice hockey)	Robert Charles Beers, (born May 20, 1967 in Pittsburgh but raised near Buffalo) is a retired American professional ice hockey defenseman. He currently serves as a radio commentator on Boston Bruins broadcasts on the WBZ Bruins radio network and is an occasional contributor to NESN Bruins and College Hockey broadcasts.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9f/Bobbeers.jpg/240px-Bobbeers.jpg
